      "subject": "Your Application for Lead Developer",
      "from": "hiring@innovatex.com",
      "date": "Thu, 10 Feb 2022 14:45:00 +0000",
      "body": "Dear John Doe,\n\nThank you for applying for the Lead Developer position with Innovatex. We appreciate the time and effort you invested in preparing and submitting your application.\n\nOur hiring team has carefully reviewed your qualifications, skills, and experience in relation to the requirements of the role. We are impressed with your background and believe you could be a strong candidate to contribute to our team.\n\nAs the next step in our hiring process, we would like to invite you to participate in a technical interview with one of our senior engineering managers. The interview will give us an opportunity to discuss your experience in greater detail and assess your technical expertise.\n\nPlease let us know your availability for the following dates:\n\n- February 15, 2022 (Tuesday), between 10:00 AM - 3:00 PM\n- February 17, 2022 (Thursday), between 2:00 PM - 6:00 PM\n\nIf the suggested time slots do not work for you, kindly provide alternative dates and times that suit your schedule, and we will do our best to accommodate you.\n\nThe interview will be conducted via Zoom, and we will provide the meeting link and further details once the schedule is confirmed. Please feel free to email us at this address, or call our recruitment coordinator directly at (123) 456-7890 if you have any questions.\n\nWe are excited about the prospect of learning more about your expertise and career goals, and we look forward to speaking with you soon.\n\nThank you again for your interest in joining Innovatex!\n\nBest regards,  \nHiring Team  \nInnovatex  \nEmail: hiring@innovatex.com  \nPhone: (123) 456-7890  \nWebsite: www.innovatex.com\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "196ca565d22b555e",
      "subject": "Re: Lead Developer Position - Salary Expectations",
      "from": "hiring@innovatex.com",
      "date": "Tue, 15 Feb 2022 09:30:00 +0000",
      "body": "Hello John,\n\nThank you for your continued interest in the Lead Developer position at InnovateX. We were impressed with your skills and experience. As part of our hiring process, we would like to understand your salary expectations for this role. Please provide us with a figure that you believe reflects your value to the team, considering your extensive experience and the responsibilities this role entails.\n\nWe look forward to your response.\n\nBest regards,\n\nAlex Rivera  \nTalent Acquisition Specialist  \nInnovateX\n"
    }
